<HEADLINE> World's longest picture </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BONN, July 3 (Xinhua) -- The "world's longest picture" was
created Saturday in and around this small German town which is
located in the south-west part of Germany.
</P>
<P>
Thousands of children and adults painted and drew on the 13.2-
kilometer-long work which wound through the town's streets and
past pastures and fields in the surrounding countryside.
</P>
<P>
The project organized by Red Cross youth volunteers will be
submitted for entry in the Guinness Book of Records. 
</P>
</TEXT>
