<HEADLINE> Tehran Stock Exchange Index Down </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
TEHRAN, July 3 (Xinhua) -- The general price index at Tehran
Stock Exchange on Saturday closed at 1,731.83 points, down 0.37
points from Wednesday's finish.
</P>
<P>
A total of 1,086,161 shares changed hands in 876 turns and the
turnover stood at 4.094 billion rials (about 1.36 million
U.S. dollars).
</P>
<P>
The shares of 18 companies made gains while those of nine
others declined. 
</P>
</TEXT>
