<HEADLINE> Tehran Stock Exchange Closes Up </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
TEHRAN, July 4 (Xinhua) -- The general price index at Tehran
Stock Exchange on Sunday closed at 1729.14 points, up 2.69 points
from Saturday's finish.
</P>
<P>
A total of 1,471,905 shares changed hands in 973 turns and the
turnover stood at 4.11 billion rials (about 1.37 million
U.S. dollars).
</P>
<P>
The shares of 21 companies made gains while those of 17 others
declined. 
