Under the draft agreement which would be finalized in
Ashkhabad, Turkmenistan next year, 100 megawatt of electricity
would be transferred in the preliminary stage to Turkey, the
Islamic Republic News Agency (IRNA) reported on Sunday.
</P>
<P>
